European Central Bank Said To Be Purchasing Italian Government Bonds Today

-- B y   P a u l   D o b s o n
-- 
2011-09-01T08:27:05Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-01/european-central-bank-said-to-be-purchasing-italian-government-bonds-today.html
The  European Central Bank  is buying
Italian securities, according to two people with knowledge of
the transactions. They declined to be identified because the
transactions are confidential.  A spokesman for the ECB declined to comment.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Paul Dobson in London at 
